etsysResourceUtilizationMIB.description: This module provides authoritative definitions for Enterasys Networks' Resource Utilization MIB.

ResourceStorageType.name: ResourceStorageType
ResourceStorageType.description: This data type is used as the syntax of the etsysResourceStorageType object in the definition of the etsysResourceStorageTable. other(1) storage type not defined by textual convention ram(2) volatile storage flash(3) nonvolatile storage usbFlash(4) nonvolatile USB stick flash storage

ResourceUtilization.name: ResourceUtilization
ResourceUtilization.description: This data type is used as the syntax for objects which report the utilization of a resource as a percentage of a defined period of time. Each value embeds the first digit to the right of the decimal, 1/10ths of a percent, by multiplying the utilization by 10. For example, a utilization of 95.7 encodes to a ResourceUtilization value of 957.

etsysResourceCpuTable.name: etsysResourceCpuTable
etsysResourceCpuTable.description: The table of processors contained in the chassis.

etsysResourceCpuEntry.name: etsysResourceCpuEntry
etsysResourceCpuEntry.description: An entry for a processor contained in the system. The entPhysicalIndex represents the chassis module the processor is contained in.

etsysResourceCpuId.name: etsysResourceCpuId
etsysResourceCpuId.description: A value assigned to the processor. Each value needs only to be unique for the module identified by the entPhysicalIndex of this entry.

etsysResourceCpuLoad5sec.name: etsysResourceCpuLoad5sec
etsysResourceCpuLoad5sec.description: The average, over the last 5 seconds, of the percentage of time that this processor was not idle.

etsysResourceCpuLoad1min.name: etsysResourceCpuLoad1min
etsysResourceCpuLoad1min.description: The average, over the last 1 minute, of the percentage of time that this processor was not idle.

etsysResourceCpuLoad5min.name: etsysResourceCpuLoad5min
etsysResourceCpuLoad5min.description: The average, over the last 5 minutes, of the percentage of time that this processor was not idle.

etsysResourceProcessTable.name: etsysResourceProcessTable
etsysResourceProcessTable.description: The table of processes running in the chassis.

etsysResourceProcessEntry.name: etsysResourceProcessEntry
etsysResourceProcessEntry.description: An entry for a process running in the chassis. The etsysResourceCpuId identifies the processor the process is running in.

etsysResourceProcessID.name: etsysResourceProcessID
etsysResourceProcessID.description: A value assigned to the process. This value is only unique per processor, not per chassis.

etsysResourceProcessName.name: etsysResourceProcessName
etsysResourceProcessName.description: A textual description of this running process.

etsysResourceProcessLoad5sec.name: etsysResourceProcessLoad5sec
etsysResourceProcessLoad5sec.description: The average, over the last 5 seconds, of the percentage of time that this process was not idle.

etsysResourceProcessLoad1min.name: etsysResourceProcessLoad1min
etsysResourceProcessLoad1min.description: The average, over the last 1 minute, of the percentage of time that this process was not idle.

etsysResourceProcessLoad5min.name: etsysResourceProcessLoad5min
etsysResourceProcessLoad5min.description: The average, over the last 5 minutes, of the percentage of time that this process was not idle.

etsysResourceStorageTable.name: etsysResourceStorageTable
etsysResourceStorageTable.description: The Table of storage utilization in the chassis.

etsysResourceStorageEntry.name: etsysResourceStorageEntry
etsysResourceStorageEntry.description: An entry for one storage area in the chassis.

etsysResourceStorageType.name: etsysResourceStorageType
etsysResourceStorageType.description: The type of storage represented by this entry.

etsysResourceStorageTypeID.name: etsysResourceStorageTypeID
etsysResourceStorageTypeID.description: A unique arbitrary value per storage type assigned to the entry.

etsysResourceStorageDescr.name: etsysResourceStorageDescr
etsysResourceStorageDescr.description: A textual description of this storage area.

etsysResourceStorageSize.name: etsysResourceStorageSize
etsysResourceStorageSize.description: The size, in Kilobytes, of the storage area.

etsysResourceStorageAvailable.name: etsysResourceStorageAvailable
etsysResourceStorageAvailable.description: The available space, in Kilobytes, left on the storage area.

etsysResource1minThreshold.name: etsysResource1minThreshold
etsysResource1minThreshold.description: The threshold for generating etsysResourceLoad1minThresholdExceeded Notifications. Setting this object to 0 will prevent the agent from generating etsysResourceCpuLoad1minThresholdExceeded notifications. When this object is set to a nonzero value, the agent will generate etsysResourceLoad1minThresholdExceeded notifications when it is detected that an etsysResourceCpuLoad1min object value has exceeded this threshold value. After the threshold has been exceeded additional notifications will be sent once a minute until the corresponding etsysResourceCpuLoad1min drops back below the threshold.

etsysResourceCpuLoad1minThresholdExceede.name: etsysResourceCpuLoad1minThresholdExceeded
etsysResourceCpuLoad1minThresholdExceede.description: This notification indicates that the average, over the last 1 minute, of the percentage of time that a processor was not idle, has exceeded the etsysResourceCpuLoad1minThreshold value.

etsysResourceUtilizationCpuGroup.name: etsysResourceUtilizationCpuGroup
etsysResourceUtilizationCpuGroup.description: A collection of objects providing basic instrumentation of CPU Resource Utilization.

etsysResourceUtilizationProcessGroup.name: etsysResourceUtilizationProcessGroup
etsysResourceUtilizationProcessGroup.description: A collection of objects providing basic instrumentation of Process Resource Utilization.

etsysResourceUtilizationStorageGroup.name: etsysResourceUtilizationStorageGroup
etsysResourceUtilizationStorageGroup.description: A collection of objects providing basic instrumentation of Storage Resource Utilization.

etsysResourceUtilizationScalarsGroup.name: etsysResourceUtilizationScalarsGroup
etsysResourceUtilizationScalarsGroup.description: A collection of objects providing basic instrumentation for Threshold configuration.

etsysResourceUtilizationCompliance.name: etsysResourceUtilizationCompliance
etsysResourceUtilizationCompliance.description: The compliance statement for devices that support the Enterasys Resource Utilization MIB.
